data.description: This absolutely stunning home features 4 bedrooms, an office, 3 full bathrooms, one half bathroom, large kitchen with separate breakfast area, a huge family room plus an over sized game room!  This home is pristine and shows like a model home. The first floor features soaring ceilings with a huge, a family room with a beautiful, cozy, electric fireplace with remote. Large primary bedroom, also on first floor has lots of windows, a large soaking tub w separate shower, private bathroom, huge walk in closet; spacious double vanities. The family room has ceiling to floor windows.  1st floor has wood grain tile, a large kitchen with all stainless steel KitchenAid appliances. Beautiful lighting fixtures, stunning quartz countertops; sprinkler system; front door with finger print/keyless entry; surveillance system, covered front porch, backyard deck, rock garden, nice size backyard and MORE!! This one looks like a model!
